   Stars coach Ken Hitchcock also reacted calmly to the loss.
</P>
<P>
   ``I thought we played well at times, and in overtime anything is
up for grabs,'' Hitchcock said. ``We knew this was going to be a
long series. It would have been nice to win this game, it could
have been this close, but we're going to have to rebound and play
even stronger.''
</P>
