   SAVINGS _ A new Missouri program, which allows residents of any
state to save money for college with significant state and federal
tax breaks, was unveiled Monday at Penn Valley Community College.
By Lynn Franey.Story will move in the ``a'' category.
</P>
<P>
   FACE _ A jury awards $9 million in damages to a man whose face
was literally torn off when a dumbwaiter fell on him while he was
making repairs in a Kansas City nursing home. By Joe Lambe. Story
will move in the ``a'' category.
</P>
<P>
   CALLCENTER _ Kansas City has become a call center hub for
thousands of employees and big companies ranging from Gateway to
ATT. By Diane Stafford. Story will move in the ``f'' category.
</P>
<P>
   STOVER _ Kansas City-based Russell Stover candies is buying
another confectioner, this one with about 200 stores. Steve Everly.
Story will move in the ``f'' category.
