   &UR; INTERNATIONAL _ (Moved in ``i'' category)  &LR;
</P>
<P>
   KOSOVO-CHINA-TRADE (Washington) _ A look at the implications of
the embassy bombing on the already-strained trade element of the
U.S.-China relationship. By David E. Sanger.
