   NBC-INTERNET (Undated) _ The proposed combination of some assets
of USA Networks, the family of cable networks, with Lycos, the
Internet portal, is about to be abandoned, said people close to the
negotiations. Meanwhile, NBC said Monday that it had agreed to
merge some of its Internet assets with Xoom, a publicly traded
electronic community that emphasizes direct marketing. By Saul
Hansell.
