<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-05-11 14:13 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2545 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-OLIPHANT-COLUMN-BOS &LR;      05-11 0775
