   ADVISORY: BETTY JAMESON STORY
</P>
<P>
   Two versions of the story about Betty Jameson, co-founder of the
LPGA, have moved from Cox News Service. The version that says she
``turns 80 today'' should not be used. The version that says she
``turned 80 Sunday'' is the correct version. If you have any
questions, call the Cox News Service in Atlanta at 404 526-5456.
</P>
