<HEADER>
A2707 &Cx1f; tad-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-HAITIANS-0512-COX     05-11 0474
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-HAITIANS-0512-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    INS ANNOUNCES REGULATIONS FOR HAITIAN REFUGEES
 &HT;    Moving in (w) Washington and (a) general news categories
 &HT;    By LARRY LIPMAN
