u v &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ELIMINATE-YUGOSLAVIA-     05-11 0032
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ELIMINATE-YUGOSLAVIA-TARGETS-BOS </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
ATTN EDITORS:  

</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   The spot budget story YUGOSLAVIA-TARGETS (i) will not move in
tonight's Boston Globe file.
