<P>
   FBN-THIEL-COLUMN (Undated) _ Art Thiel writes on the death of
former Dallas Cowboys offensive lineman Mark Tuinei and the
so-called Texas Heroin Massacre. There are lessons in Plano, Texas,
for all of us.
</P>
<P>
   By Art Thiel. (Story will move in the ``s'' category.)
</P>
</TEXT>
