<P>
   _ Readers who feel that Nitro, the World Championship Wrestling
scent, is too, well, hormonal and not enough cerebral should
consider Pi, the new Givenchy scent advertised with the line
``Intelligence is the new seducer.'' For those who don't remember
geometry, pi has nothing to do with the Biotic Baking Brigade and
everything to do with the circumference of a circle.
</P>
