<P>
   WNBA-SEATTLE (Seattle) _ When the American Basketball League
abruptly shut down last December, women's basketball fans in
Seattle had one glimmer of hope: The WNBA might expand its league
here. On Tuesday, city officials confirmed that hope is alive _
with conditions attached.
